# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# open-research-skills .gitignore
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# This repository is a curated collection of skill markdown
# files. It is intended to be plain text + YAML only — no
# build artifacts, no AI session state, no editor state.
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# ── AI assistant / agent session state ──────────────────────
# Claude Code
.claude/
.claude.json
.claude.jsonl
**/CLAUDE.md
**/claude.md

# Other AI assistants (only ignore lowercase, generic agent configs)
# Note: AGENTS.md (uppercase) at the repo root or in skills/ is ours, keep it.
**/agents.md
.cursor/
.aider*
.gemini/
.copilot/
.codeium/
.cody/
.codyaa/
.tabby/
continue/
.windsurf/
.crush/
.codigger/

# Generic AI cache/state patterns
**/.ai/
**/.assistant/
**/.copilot/
**/.llm/
**/ai-cache/
**/llm-cache/

